Class GUI

    public class GUI
extends javax.swing.JFrame
    The Class creates the graphical user interface and uses the Adapter to fill itself with the data out of the database.

    • Constructor Detail

      • GUI

        public GUI()
        The constructor invokes methods which initialize the different components of the GUI. It also invokes methods which use the DatabaseAdapter in order to fill the components with the data of the database.
